URL = http://shareshed.org.uk

=Description=

"People are drowning in stuff and the world is covered in trash. The newly opened Share Shed Totnes, supported by the Network of Wellbeing, is one solution focused approach to this issue. It’s basically a “library of things” where you can borrow useful items like: DIY tools, camping and gardening equipment, sporting equipment and more!"


=More Information=

- To find out more about Share Shed Totnes, you can visit shareshed.org.uk.

